'''''With Friends Like These...''''' is a 1998 film by [[Philip Frank Messina]]. It stars [[Robert Costanzo]], [[Jon Tenney]], [[David Strathairn]] and [[Adam Arkin]], and features a cameo by [[Bill Murray]].  

==Summary==

In the film, four small-time two-bit character actors (Costanzo, Tenney Strathairn and Arkin), all close friends, are competing for same important part in the next Martin Scorsese mob film.

